Global Influenza Vaccine Market Insights
Influenza Vaccine Market size was valued at USD 5.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Influenza Vaccine Market Overview
The global influenza vaccine market was valued at approximately USD 6.5 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 10.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing awareness regarding the importance of immunization and the rising demand for preventive measures against seasonal flu. Governments and health organizations worldwide continue to promote influenza vaccination campaigns, significantly contributing to market expansion. Factors such as technological advancements in vaccine development, along with rising incidences of influenza-related complications, also play a key role in market growth.

